    "description": "A maintenance-truth lane carries a Stable (or LTS) claim only when its maintenance scorecard passes every dimension (backport policy, hotfix policy, proof freshness, evidence expiry, Help/About truth, and docs truth), the Help/About support posture is disclosed, the proof packet is current within its freshness SLO, any waiver is unexpired, the owner manifest is signed, and its downgrade automation is defined and its frozen-fallback rollback plan verified. A lane that loses any of those must drop below the cutline rather than inherit an adjacent certified lane."
  },
